{"id":232728361,"title":"你說想成為誰的太陽","content":"https://i.imgur.com/mgRbBRh.jpg\n\n你說想成為誰的太陽\n在冰冷的宇宙裡為他發亮\n\n「沒有人是不需要溫暖的」\n對付出的信仰脹成偌大的質量\n重力坍塌之際\n你縱身躍入閃爍的渾沌\n卻從此迷失了座標\n\n你知道自己不是太陽\n萬里之外也沒有綠洲\n但你必須深信\n每一分付出都是有價值的\n\n氫氣燃盡的數光年\n巧遇幽靜清澈的夜空\n詩人為你編織故事\n\n那是一顆想成為太陽的星星\n最後只成了自己的太陽\n\n我的唉居：\nhttps://www.instagram.com/p/B6TUNoSDirY/?igshid=1n1agtulsqron","excerpt":"你說想成為誰的太陽，在冰冷的宇宙裡為他發亮，「沒有人是不需要溫暖的」對付出的信仰脹成偌大的質量，重力坍塌之際，你縱身躍入閃爍的渾沌，卻從此迷失了座標，你知道自己不是太陽，萬里之外也沒有綠洲，但你必須深","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"f8acd3e6-17e9-4d9d-bc7c-bf24d94c2ad1","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-12-20T17:05:55.252Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-20T17:05:55.252Z","commentCount":0,"likeCount":13,"tags":[],"topics":["創作","文字","詩文","隨筆","心情"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"詩文","forumAlias":"literature","school":"冬片微微","department":"anothert","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":null,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":13}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/mgRbBRh.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"6c689359-80db-4290-bec5-4a2f143e6533","url":"https://i.imgur.com/mgRbBRhl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/mgRbBRhl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/mgRbBRhl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-20T17:05:55.252Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-20T17:05:55.252Z"},{"id":"6c689359-80db-4290-bec5-4a2f143e6533","url":"https://i.imgur.com/mgRbBRh.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/mgRbBRh","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/mgRbBRhl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-12-20T17:05:55.252Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-20T17:05:55.252Z"}],"postAvatar":""}